  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. The model is intended to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 2. Full 13-factor assessment: 7 factors assessed (all meeting required levels), 6 factors not assessed (acceptable at MRL 2). Packaged under ProfileMinimal; structured context-of-use linkage is captured in the Claim and Requirement prose below.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/morrison-cpb-hemolysis-mrl2",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/morrison-cpb-cfd-hemolysis-worst-case",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/fda-generic-cbp-cfd-hemolysis-v3",
  "bindsDataset": [
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/fda-cbp-experimental-hemolysis-2019",
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/morrison-mesh-sensitivity-study-2022"
  ],
