    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at this risk level per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 1. The CFD hemolysis model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in CPB service (Class II device, adult cardiac output range 4–6 L/min). Decision is accepted with no outstanding corrective actions.",
